name: TinaKeen Workshop
description:
**Non Sale Price is $599. This $200 saving is for the first 3 people to sign up. 

TK Wedding Workshop will be October 4 & 5, 2013 in Angleton Texas at Out Under The Trees. 

This workshop is a portfolio building event filled with a stylized over the top wedding theme. Shoots include morning bridals and a full evening wedding. One theme, 2-8 fully styled models, one gorgeous location and lots of fun and meals provided.
